---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import PageHero from '../components/PageHero.astro';
import ContactForm from '../components/ContactForm.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Services — Damien Herlihy"
  description="Notion templates and one-to-one PKM coaching for teachers, from a language school owner and PKM nerd."
>
  <section class="services-page container page-content">
    <PageHero
      eyebrow="Services"
      description="I'm something of a personal knowledge management (PKM) nerd. Marie Kondo, David Allen, Marie Poulin, and Tiago Forte have been my guiding lights in this space."
    >
      Templates <em>&amp;</em> coaching
    </PageHero>

    <div class="services-prose prose" data-reveal>
      <p>
        In the area of PKM my go-to-tool is
        <a href="https://www.notion.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Notion</a>.
      </p>

      <h2>What is Notion?</h2>
      <p>
        It's a single space where you can think, write, and plan. Notion is like building
        with LEGO blocks: you can easily assemble, rearrange, and customize anything in it,
        unlike a traditional Word document, which is more like a fixed, printed page.
      </p>

      <h3>Let me tell you.</h3>
      <p>
        I've made Notion my life for the past year, so you don't have to! During that year I
        created a range of templates that run my business, and my life too. I share what
        I've learned through two main services: templates and one-to-one coaching.
      </p>

      <h2>Templates</h2>
      <p>
        My paid and free templates are found at
        <a href="https://www.languagelayouts.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Language Layouts</a>.
      </p>

      <h2>Coaching</h2>
      <p>
        Also, I do coaching. I help teachers get organised. We cover the core ideas of PKM
        and at the end of it all you'll have a one of a kind Notion workspace. Something you
        can use to organise your teaching business online. I charge 999 USD dollars for this
        experience. I only have six slots per year. As this is a new service, my first three
        clients will get this service for $500 USD.
      </p>

      <h3>Why is this a good deal?</h3>
      <p>
        I'm the type of person who always wants to please. Owing to that embedded
        personality trait I will always provide you with significantly more value than what
        you have paid.
      </p>
      <p>
        Also, I'm in a sweet spot in terms of my experience. I have built a successful
        language school, I have an extensive knowledge of PKM, and I have invested one year
        to become highly proficient in Notion.
      </p>
      <p>
        If you are interested in this service contact me below and we can chat. Plus, I can
        share some extra documents about the coaching experience too.
      </p>

      <h3>Oh!</h3>
      <p>
        One more thing. I'm moving onto my
        '<a href="https://www.amazon.com/Second-Mountain-David-Brooks/dp/0812993268" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Second Mountain</a>'.
        After taking care of running expenses, all proceeds I earn from this venture will be
        donated to charity. My aim is to commit 10% of my overall income - across all my
        businesses - to charity.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="services-contact" data-reveal>
      <ContactForm />
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .services-prose {
    margin-bottom: 60px;
  }

  .services-contact {
    max-width: 700px;
  }
</style>
